<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=utf-8" http-equiv=Content-Type></meta>
  <title>Схема</title>
  <style>
    html, body {
      background-color: #fcfaeb;
      height: 100%;
      margin: 0;
      width: 100%;
    }
    html {
      display: table;
    }
    body {
      color: #413003;
      display: table-cell;
      font-family: 'MS Sans Serif', Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: normal;
      text-align: center;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
    #scheme-tables-position {
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
      }
    #scheme-tables-list {
      display: inline-table;
      height: 200px;
      position: relative;
      width: 300px;
    }
    .scheme-table-body {
      background-color: white;
      border: 1px solid #b3ac86;
      border-bottom-left-radius: 3px;
      border-bottom-right-radius: 3px;
      border-top-left-radius: 3px;
      border-top-right-radius: 3px;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: absolute;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .scheme-table-title {
      background-color: #b3ac86;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .scheme-table-number {
      font-size: 14px;
      height: auto !important;
      height: 17px;
      min-height: 17px;
    }
    .scheme-table-number.checkbox-mode {
      background: url(data:image/png;base64,) left no-repeat;
    }
    .scheme-table-number.checkbox-mode:hover {
      background: url(data:image/png;base64,) left no-repeat;
    }
    .scheme-table-number.checkbox-mode:active {
      background: url(data:image/png;base64,) left no-repeat;
    }
    .scheme-table-number.checkbox-mode.checked {
      background: url(data:image/png;base64,) left no-repeat;
    }
    .scheme-table-number.checkbox-mode.checked:hover {
      background: url(data:image/png;base64,) left no-repeat;
    }
    .scheme-table-number.checkbox-mode.checked:active {
      background: url(data:image/png;base64,) left no-repeat;
    }
    .scheme-plan-element {
      background-color: black;
      font-size: 0px;
      height: 0px;
      position: absolute;
      width: 0px;
    }
    .scheme-plan-wall {
      background-color: #b3ac86;
    }
    .scheme-plan-block {
      background-color: #f7efde;
      border: #b3ac86 solid 2px;
    }
    ins.scheme-reserve-ins {
      color: #413003;
      display: inline-block;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    div.scheme-reserve-div {
      cursor: pointer;
      float: left;
      width: 7em;
    }
    span.scheme-reserve-left {
      display: inline;
      float: left;
      margin: 0;
      text-align: right;
      width: 3em;
    }
    span.scheme-reserve-center {
      display: inline;
      float: left;
      margin: 0;
      text-align: center;
      width: 1em;
    }
    span.scheme-reserve-right {
      display: inline;
      float: left;
      margin: 0;
      text-align: left;
    }
  </style>
  <!--[if gt IE 6]>
  <style>
    #scheme-tables-position {
      margin-top: expression( this . parentNode . offsetHeight > this . offsetHeight ?(( this . parentNode . offsetHeight-this . offsetHeight ) / 2 + "px" ) : "0" );
    }
  </style>
  <![endif]<!-->
  <style type="text/css">
    {Style}
  </style>
  <style type="text/css">
    {CSS}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div id=scheme-tables-position class="[Class]" style="[Style]">
    <div id=scheme-tables-list>
      {Items}
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
